{"tid":28511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「置頂」即刻同我坐直條腰！！！","createTime":"2016-12-08T03:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T01:41:49.000Z","uid":30411,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7903e114b3e709ebcb39516688956d67dc76513a","tid":28511,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"坐直！！ 後腰用力！！ 放低條二郎腿唔好蹺腳！！<br />\n<br />\n鬆下個膊頭！！ 深呼吸！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個二個廢青當自己身體係消耗品<br />\n<br />\n懶後生乜都唔理<br />\n<br />\n屌你唔好咁天真啦<br />\n<br />\n你睇下隔離team個個坐到直不甩，精神爽利，從來都無人叫過腰痛，連最廢個個Peter都識得間中起身伸個懶腰呀<br />\n<br />\n你第時腰酸背痛<br />\n<br />\n你第時寒背縮骨<br />\n<br />\n你而家精神萎靡<br />\n<br />\n你間中頭痛，你見暈，你面色唔好，你無黎胃口<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你無坐直個人呀！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n成米蝦米咁卷起個人血液點循環呀！！ 肌鍵點伸展呀！！ 細細粒尾龍骨支撐住你半個身幾十公斤既重量呀！！！腰間盤突出點算呀！！<br />\n<br />\n喂坐好啲唔駛錢架，蹺腳好型咩？ 攣起個身黎做野有效率啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n即刻去廁所洗個面伸伸手伸伸腳啦望！！！<br />\n<br />\n番黎同我坐番好呀！！"},{"pid":"3b24f6d0807368a93021d7e6aa16205c79161e89","tid":28511,"uid":56095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 精神 精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313c3ef0f0be51027b85041eda4cf32e06502756","tid":28511,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"屙緊屎呀屌"},{"pid":"7f3ac6c97854a6ee7a0a321167e13ef3b3cc01d9","tid":28511,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a3a05c6e05fc5bd5ca108a355f65b0bf70b5fd","tid":28511,"uid":37254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"