食緊川味都挺挺腰先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打食邊間川味?  建生?"},{"pid":"ccc857fe56e0ce10752b79cc8ae64e01d78f7174","tid":28511,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:59:44.000Z","msg":"見到即刻坐直左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eb196df842194108b022c62c1c901a2600e698","tid":28511,"uid":18508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:00:01.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打，立即直左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e054b062960ad1f92551d4fd279815f07e547318","tid":28511,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"訓係度睇緊呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683562934892ee8e4c830c6da1c79dc2a7d39d27","tid":28511,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係直左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爽左"},{"pid":"52db24c2738ae10f7e8a7498e1511a25b89053ff","tid":28511,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"馬上挺直左 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推一推等大家都直啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acaa7722e2172f5b376638f2a44309a5d6234bb","tid":28511,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"食飽飯唔駛坐直呀而家？ 用力！！！"},{"pid":"826cb131159dc41556925aa5c0f7938d7a0108b6","tid":28511,"uid":22359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"即刻坐返直條腰 多謝巴打提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2abf21ae169359469140fc8447954f0826a4e9b","tid":28511,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687102af06ddbe7a45eb319da491f5961ea78867","tid":28511,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:06:01.000Z","msg":"即時直左"},{"pid":"a87973fefd03c08d83474246698b01d4b034720a","tid":28511,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"你自己就坐直左啦, 好得閒呀可?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識唔識幫下同team啲人呀? 幫手提下佢地挺直腰板啦<br />\n<br />\n除左你之外大把人未夠數呀!!!!!!!!! 自己到數就係度玩手指!!<br />\n<br />\n咁樣我點升你呀?! 又話要搏要紮!!!  <br />\n<br />\n呢個post 沉得快過你既健康指數呀!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n坐直左個人就幫手推post等多D人受到鼓勵啦仲望!!!"},{"pid":"fa5c8d032cb55ab0b5cc8d6e06a0c22e9aaa5bc2","tid":28511,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:47:44.000Z","msg":"頸痛點算呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09033730489030aad8aced805cf8137a3d67fa70","tid":28511,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448821fa8c7a4b28580fe8721535125d475cb479","tid":28511,"uid":15580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已坐直 多謝巴打"},{"pid":"0b7e28906cca77d9017fd359d911979306934eb6","tid":28511,"uid":42442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9def3e54c0654fac479d1b69f13177eea1c66103","tid":28511,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頸痛點算呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢度主要屌下大家腰板唔直，不過你咁上進我都好欣賞，我作為前輩會盡力幫下你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都市人頸痛最普遍兩個原因：dup低頭太多/睡姿唔好<br />\n<br />\n低頭問題大家都耳熟能詳，玩電話，用電腦，睇雜誌，坐巴士訓覺，全部都係dup低頭既活動<br />\n<br />\n你個頭其實重過粒西瓜，條頸肌肉又少，中樞神經又多，咁脆弱既地方長期幫你拎住個頭唔攰架？ 你試下捧住粒西瓜兩個鐘睇下對手痛唔痛？ 岳高個頭啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外好多人鐘意懶健康去買高級枕頭，又波浪紋又磁石又記憶海棉又人體工學，有軟有硬<br />\n<br />\n但係偏偏無人注意枕頭高度！！！！<br />\n<br />\n枕頭太高太矮都會令頸部肌肉長期緊張，訓醒衰過無訓！！<br />\n<br />\n嚴重啲你膊頭會痺<br />\n<br />\n你對手會痺<br />\n<br />\n你頭痛，你頸痛，你訓得唔好，你點坐都唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n可能就係枕頭出事！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n試下換個扁啲既訓幾晚！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n搞極唔得就睇醫生！！"},{"pid":"2f8a839fa41838683ad541640ac5a7a7bb288838","tid":28511,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"巴打做營養師？"},{"pid":"2f0a265a97b88129c1c195181598d02eca9660ad","tid":28511,"uid":14001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"即刻醒返晒"},{"pid":"d779204b55eff8c4e45674ba6da9af1a7276f98a","tid":28511,"uid":28574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"c8595f2ac97ef977d77e5bc5614c0d12941f15d0","tid":28511,"uid":40931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:45:32.000Z","msg":"多謝 巴打 行路都企直咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4857480d051d72cbb944ea877ea28c3c0209f09e","tid":28511,"uid":56095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"推 我按摩師建議 訓教唔用枕頭有助寒背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad93395ff604cb737c445e4c57cc8026509a5b10","tid":28511,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"57bf0317eac13f6ba0fa7b1cf59e2e94915b3f59","tid":28511,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:41:54.000Z","msg":"話時話好似換左床褥之後先開始持續痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69eef10edff48794720f104552c7b71381c480c2","tid":28511,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"旗都直埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dca237646c9b196515742c50f2c0a6f74608a3e","tid":28511,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc98ec0f17848761310fc7decf40c3df201bad5f","tid":28511,"uid":54016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"即刻坐返直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31863dba53af867cbae2e3e17fde77b8d9bfb55","tid":28511,"uid":1815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家坐翻直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85416725d34eb784126eb47020effa5bd2ab3148","tid":28511,"uid":17753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"精神仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abf3f109009e4e5ce4d2bf7ae116996d4be1497","tid":28511,"uid":26463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20