 /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪床褥太淋？？！！<br />\n<br />\n出面有啲幾百蚊一張既床墊，有軟有硬，姨媽傢私好似都有<br />\n<br />\n鋪係新床褥上面調節下<br />\n<br />\n唔好因爲懶搞到變肌肉勞捐<br />\n<br />\n聽日星期六就搞搞佢！！！"},{"pid":"8b4660f654629edb47bb099e7998af55db1c9c13","tid":28511,"uid":36756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f88ae53be5cc8a6851970615ce3d04f0bb2a6b9","tid":28511,"uid":3734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}